# Authentication Flow

This application uses Microsoft Authentication Library (MSAL) for authentication with Microsoft services.

## Key Files

- **Auth Configuration**: [ms-teams-app/src/config/authConfig.ts](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/config/authConfig.ts) - MSAL configuration
- **Login Page**: [ms-teams-app/src/pages/Login.tsx](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/pages/Login.tsx) - Login page component
- **Login Button**: [ms-teams-app/src/components/LoginButton.tsx](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/components/LoginButton.tsx) - Login button component
- **Logout Button**: [ms-teams-app/src/components/LogoutButton.tsx](mdc:ms-teams-app/src/components/LogoutButton.tsx) - Logout button component

Authentication is handled through the MsalProvider in the App component with protected routes using AuthenticatedTemplate and UnauthenticatedTemplate components.
